    <article class="mb-10 pb-8 border-b border-base-300">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">The Economic Impact of Entrepreneurial Alumni: University of Virginia</h3>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-2">With Michael Lenox, Andrew King, and Asif Mehedi · UVA Darden Batten Institute (2014)</div>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-3">
        The third in the alumni-impact trilogy (after MIT 2009 and Stanford 2012), applying the same methodology to UVA. Survey of more than 135,000 UVA alumni (22,757 valid responses) found 65,000 alumni-founded companies, 2.3 million employees worldwide, and an estimated $1.6 trillion in annual global revenues.
      </p>
      <a href="https://web3.darden.virginia.edu/uva-alumni/download/U.Va.%20Entrepreneurial%20Alumni.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link text-sm">Read the full report (PDF) ↗</a>
